<div class="blogCard card border-6 shadow p-3 mb-5 bg-white rounded">
    <div class="card-body">
      <h3 class="card-title">Blog title</h3>
      <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">username possibly</h6>
      <p class="card-text">
        UserPostBody with substr(start, finish) Some quick example text to build
        on the card title and make up the bulk of the card's content ... &nbsp;
        <a href="#" class="card-link">Read More..</a>
      </p>
      <div class="mb-1 text-muted">22/2/6 Date Created</div>
    </div>
